    },
    {
      "start": 562.74,
      "end": 565.36,
      "text": "굉장히 적극적인 이웃이었죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 565.82,
      "end": 567.92,
      "text": "여기서 drop by, drop by."
    },
    {
      "start": 568.32,
      "end": 569.28,
      "text": "이게 무슨 뜻일까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 570.1,
      "end": 570.34,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 570.62,
      "end": 572.3,
      "text": "들르다 라는 의미입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 572.92,
      "end": 574.48,
      "text": "You should drop by tonight."
    },
    {
      "start": 574.9,
      "end": 576.6,
      "text": "오늘 밤에 들러요."
    },
    {
      "start": 576.86,
      "end": 577.84,
      "text": "라는 해석이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 578.46,
      "end": 579.48,
      "text": "이 부분 확인해 보세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 579.48,
      "end": 582.46,
      "text": "Hey, you don't play poker, do you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 582.56,
      "end": 584.7,
      "text": "Because I run a weekly game."
    },
    {
      "start": 584.82,
      "end": 587.46,
      "text": "And we could sure use another player."
    },
    {
      "start": 587.46,
      "end": 591.72,
      "text": "It's all very hush-hush because gambling's not allowed around here."
    },
    {
      "start": 591.8,
      "end": 593.24,
      "text": "Like most things that are worthwhile."
    },
    {
      "start": 593.64,
      "end": 595.22,
      "text": "You should drop by tonight."
    },
    {
      "start": 595.38,
      "end": 596.62,
      "text": "And say hi to the guys."
    },
    {
      "start": 596.7,
      "end": 598.22,
      "text": "God, you know, it's been a very..."
    },
    {
      "start": 598.22,
      "end": 599.96,
      "text": "Look, it's a long day for me."
    },
    {
      "start": 600.02,
      "end": 600.84,
      "text": "I just moved in."
    },
    {
      "start": 601.02,
      "end": 601.5,
      "text": "But thanks."
    },
    {
      "start": 601.58,
      "end": 602.58,
      "text": "I really appreciate you."
    },
    {
      "start": 603.1,
      "end": 604.18,
      "text": "The invitation is sweet."
    },
    {
      "start": 604.18,
      "end": 608.59,
      "text": "네, 이렇게 스크린 잉글리쉬 복습해봤습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 609.45,
      "end": 611.91,
      "text": "누가 봐도 내양적인 마을사인데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 612.49,
      "end": 616.33,
      "text": "반면에 다들 극도로 외향적인 성격을 보이던"
    },
    {
      "start": 616.33,
      "end": 618.53,
      "text": "그 선 스프링스타운의 이웃들이었잖아요."
    }
  ]
}